OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FKatie Price tells her sister Sophie
OL,8,Fthat her husband is alive and that she
OL,9,Fhad a one minute phone call with him
OL,10,Fas he was held in custody. Credit: The
OL,11,FKatie Price Show
OL,13,FKatie Price says that she has finally
OL,14,Ffound out what happened to her
OL,15,Fhusband, around two weeks after he
OL,16,Fwent missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
