OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FThe former glamour model and reality
OL,8,FTV star claimed on Thursday that Lee
OL,9,FAndrews had been interrogated on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of being "a spy" and that
OL,11,Fshe had finally had the chance to have
OL,12,Fa one-minute phone call with him.
OL,14,FWhile she did not mention what country
OL,15,FAndrews was being detained in nor who
OL,16,Fwas interrogating him, the Foreign
OL,17,FOffice said it was supporting the
OL,18,Ffamily of a British man in Dubai after
OL,19,FPrice revealed her husband was missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
