OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779995467
OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FPrice previously said she had been in
OL,8,Fcontact with police in Dubai after
OL,9,FAndrews, who lives in the United Arab
OL,10,FEmirates (UAE) failed to contact her
OL,11,Ffor days.
OL,13,F"Today was the day ` which is why I'm
OL,14,Fhappy ` Lee has been found alive," she
OL,15,Ftold the Katie Price Show podcast on
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
