PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779995467
OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"I don't know the full update. All I
OL,8,Fknow is ` they thought he was a spy `
OL,9,Fso he's been interrogated... I am
OL,10,Fhappy today because I didn't know what
OL,11,Fhad happened, where he had gone, but
OL,12,Fhe has been found alive."
OL,14,FPrice said she only had one minute
OL,15,Fwith her husband on the phone.
OL,16,FRelating the conversation, she added
OL,17,F"they thought he was a spy, he's been
OL,18,Finterrogated, had hoods on him" but
OL,19,Fshe did not say who "they" referred to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
