OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FAddressing speculation about Andrews
OL,8,Ffollowing another woman on Instagram
OL,9,Fduring this period, Price told her
OL,10,Fpodcast: "I did ask him. He hasn't
OL,11,Fbeen on his phone.
OL,13,F"He hasn't had his phone. He's been
OL,14,Finterrogated they've gone through his
OL,15,Fphone. So, they've been mucking about
OL,16,Fon his phone basically, it's not Lee,
OL,17,Fhe hasn't got his phone.
OL,26,@rD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
