OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"What happened with that other woman
OL,8,Fwas apparently she activated her
OL,9,Faccount and maybe she followed Lee or
OL,10,FLee followed her years ago or whenever.
OL,12,F"They've never exchanged messages or
OL,13,Fnothing. So, she blocked him. That's
OL,14,Fwhy it's gone back."
OL,16,FWhen she confronted Lee about the
OL,17,Fwoman, Price suggested her husband did
OL,18,Fnot know what she was talking about.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
