OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779995467
OL,3,C'They thought he was a spy': Katie
OL,4,CPrice says she's spoken to missing
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,F"I said it's been a bloody nightmare,
OL,8,Fit's gone viral, this that. And he
OL,9,Fsaid to me did you think I was dead,
OL,10,FI'm like 'yes, we didn't know what had
OL,11,Fhappened'. But it doesn't sound like
OL,12,Fhe had a good time, put it that way.
OL,14,F"When he gets out, we'll get the real
OL,15,Fstory of everything that happened.
OL,16,FIt's going to be like Lee this is the
OL,17,Ftime now. There's so much speculation
OL,18,Fabout you, it's about time you
OL,19,Factually do a sit-down interview... I
OL,20,Fthink the public deserve it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
